          Terms of Service
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400">
          Last updated: January 2025
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-stone dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <h2>Agreement to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing and using {SITE.name}, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.
          If you disagree with any part of these terms, you may not access the website.
