        <p>
          <strong>Important:</strong> The travel information, including but not limited to prices,
          schedules, conditions, and safety information, is subject to change without notice.
          We strongly recommend that you:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Verify all information before making travel decisions</li>
          <li>Check current conditions and requirements with local authorities</li>
          <li>Obtain appropriate travel insurance</li>
          <li>Exercise caution and use your own judgment when engaging in any activities</li>
        </ul>

